if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽落唔抵屌</blockquote><br />\n仲要衰老強有連登仔支持<br />\n衰打劫只會俾人屌冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n衰老強 連登仔：勞資糾紛/條女係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n衰打劫 連登仔：廢柴 垃圾 連登求其一個都月入百萬 呢條友一定無上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cbb0a38244bd435800fa993a87642bd29176bad","tid":465833,"uid":14201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:17:26.000Z","msg":"收銀機會有幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一多少少錢就清機啦 仲擺係收銀機畀你打劫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773f3e6028952d5610f5f75f19324302f5ddb60f","tid":465833,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"見慣風雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba535a90f4480da70d4777b7499eaea2aa521653","tid":465833,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:34:39.000Z","msg":"其實又岩 <br />\n你唔開機佢地拎唔到錢<br />\n佢地開錢殺你自己又多十幾廿碌<br />\n有無人會為左收銀機錢最多幾皮野而衰老謀？<br />\n只要你臨危不亂 賊一定走先過你<br />\n<br />\n阿嬸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff86f42160679bdf0f96765a94549c8340b284cc","tid":465833,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:36:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"614414adeff1ef15b2df6abc9223b3b167bf4238","tid":465833,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:42:59.000Z","msg":"賊：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/12/184256_9f1e1f672c11194dae40e90a734adefa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F12%2F184256_9f1e1f672c11194dae40e90a734adefa.jpg&h=d5b5a24e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dd176cc4fdc88680284302b532439eb1b7a390c","tid":465833,"uid":7843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:21:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係香港打劫7-11真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蠢撚到去7仔打劫仲要有cam對撚住你個衰樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係要做犯法搵錢的話偷野未仲撚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蠢撚真係蠢撚"},{"pid":"10ed2a9a799f155aeff4004686dd9d8402d09105","tid":465833,"uid":157898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:25:44.000Z","msg":"白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134f4e27e9b0f9bdfb8dc9e5d51e87a0b4e379ec","tid":465833,"uid":619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:34:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實又岩 <br />\n你唔開機佢地拎唔到錢<br />\n佢地開錢殺你自己又多十幾廿碌<br />\n有無人會為左收銀機錢最多幾皮野而衰老謀？<br />\n只要你臨危不亂 賊一定走先過你<br />\n<br />\n阿嬸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢得0.1%會劈你都唔好博啦<br />\n啲錢又唔係你嘅"},{"pid":"a47ec94a399d5eab689bd35b7c77640eb6673cb4","tid":465833,"uid":13845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:36:52.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 9幾年王晶啲戲劇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bf1ede6c5712b2240432ba0aa2cf47face702e","tid":465833,"uid":29093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:56:32.000Z","msg":"「唔好玩啦」依句真係屈機 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有個你唔鍾意既人向你表白 , 都可以用「唔好玩啦」收佢皮"},{"pid":"b0e6092d1e17c16430dcd58241511ac9e1dbdf49","tid":465833,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:58:49.000Z","msg":"男職員驚，女職員反而唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9215f0ba3c04a9e44c2c6a4ceb3f0082dd968a6","tid":465833,"uid":77318,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T12:16:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係香港打劫7-11真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢先最聰明<br />\n梗有一間喺左近，夠方便<br />\n坐監唔洗比3000租床位<br />\n又唔洗比錢水電煤食飯<br />\n無所事事佢又有安排比你<br />\n免費職業培訓<br />\n想繼續住就唔守規矩<br />\n正呀"},{"pid":"fbf53d9f79f6fdc9c3545b81ab8e586fd38b0280","tid":465833,"uid":14591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T12:20:30.000Z","msg":"係香港打劫？<br />\n警犬 all around you"},{"pid":"a02633d3fa8a9dc8c6aa0c99d0162708bbf494c4","tid":465833,"uid":84116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T12:20:53.000Z","msg":"7仔d cam好似廢廢地，d解象度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b5e24d45f453da555273543124ee931c9b556c","tid":465833,"uid":3694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T12:31:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>返過7仔就知<br />\n通常一夠5千，職員就會將啲錢放入夾萬<br />\n所以收銀機啲錢多極有限</blockquote><br />\n我通常等臨收工先一次過三萬咁入袋,個感覺好爽</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夜更咁做實比經理屌到傻。以前試過多過兩千唔入袋都俾人屌。"},{"pid":"55b1bab5e9cac7d631cb2a0522fc9cbc925e6427","tid":465833,"uid":119008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T12:41:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呀姐原來未有60<br />\n成日ot 完都見佢自己一個返夜<br />\n今次好彩有人陪<br />\n<br />\n勿相認</blockquote><br />\n每更7仔起碼會有兩個人架<br />\n一個倉一個收銀 細極都會有兩個人"},{"pid":"67da7be5a49165de0da1e8d5e3ed5b6725486e45","tid":465833,"uid":1911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T12:50:15.000Z","msg":"以為吉野家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614f9b578e1fb400b537f9af6a95d560dc99d72e","tid":465833,"uid":46086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T12:51:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賊：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/12/184256_9f1e1f672c11194dae40e90a734adefa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F12%2F184256_9f1e1f672c11194dae40e90a734adefa.jpg&h=d5b5a24e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇人理你"},{"pid":"f1e9bed51d2f1e855d07fa85f7ae0edcccb3bd5c","tid":465833,"uid":89696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T12:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係香港打劫7-11真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一日收入唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收銀機唔會擺太多銀紙,一過五六千就會入落夾萬。"},{"pid":"e6d8e268e970295b42e4a081b5daf3bb5d5bf297","tid":465833,"uid":145194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:11:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>返過7仔就知<br />\n通常一夠5千，職員就會將啲錢放入夾萬<br />\n所以收銀機啲錢多極有限</blockquote><br />\n我通常等臨收工先一次過三萬咁入袋,個感覺好爽</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夜更咁做實比經理屌到傻。以前試過多過兩千唔入袋都俾人屌。</blockquote><br />\n中更，月頭月中d人瘋狂交費幾千幾千咁交，交一條隊已經一萬，二三千入一次袋嘅話，一日要入幾多個袋，你地就真係唔好玩啦"}]}